sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Root as Root state s_cf0
  participant Cand as Candidate generator
  participant Oracle as Target RRI oracle
  participant Policy as Rollout policy
  participant Store as Replay / Zarr store
  participant QH as Q_H learner
  participant Eval as Oracle-rescored evaluator

  Root->>Cand: generate Q_t, m_t, rho_t
  Cand->>Oracle: valid candidates and target descriptor
  Oracle-->>Policy: r_t^e(i), labels, optional lookahead scores
  Policy->>Policy: choose a_t by random-valid, greedy, lookahead, or softmax
  Policy->>Root: transition P_{t+1}=P_t union P_{q_t}
  Policy->>Cand: regenerate Q_{t+1}, m_{t+1}, rho_{t+1}
  Policy->>Store: write replay row with mask, action, reward, next state
  Store->>QH: sample minibatch with valid-action masks
  QH->>QH: i_star = argmax_i Q_theta(s_{t+1}, q_{t+1,i}) over valid i
  QH->>QH: y_t = r_t^e + gamma(1-d_t) Q_target(s_{t+1}, q_{t+1,i_star})
  QH->>Store: log predictions, losses, calibration, invalidity
  QH->>Eval: deploy pi_Q on held-out roots
  Eval->>Oracle: oracle-rescore selected action sequence
  Oracle-->>Eval: J_e^H, G_t^H, eta_Q, scene RRI, cost
